doc.previous: The codified local laws are contained in the New York City Administrative Code in 29 titles 475 476 477 the regulations promulgated by city agencies are compiled in the Rules of the City of New York in 71 titles 478 and The City Record is the official journal published each weekday except legal holidays 479 480
doc.after: Each borough is coextensive with a judicial district of the New York Supreme Court and hosts other state and city courts Manhattan also hosts the Supreme Court Appellate Division First Department while Brooklyn hosts the Appellate Division Second Department
